OL,3,CMan dies after house fire in Dunmurry
OL,5,FA man in his fifties has died
OL,6,Ffollowing a fire at a house in
OL,7,FDunmurry.
OL,9,FAll three emergency services attended
OL,10,Fthe blaze at a house in Station View,
OL,11,Fwhich was reported at around 8:40pm on
OL,12,FMonday.
OL,14,FPolice are continuing to look into the
OL,15,Fcircumstances of the fire, however, at
OL,16,Fthis time it is not being treated as
OL,17,Fsuspicious.
OL,19,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,20,FITVX
